summary: Completed comprehensive backend API testing for DocFlow document management system. All 7 required endpoints tested successfully. Gemini 2.5 Flash integration working correctly for document analysis. 117 documents in database with extracted data (valor, tercero). PDF generation and download functionality working properly.

minor_issues.issue: No batch suggestions found despite having documents with extracted data
minor_issues.impact: Algorithm may be too strict requiring exact valor matches within 1%

passed_tests: GET /api/documents/list - Shows 117 documents with extracted data
GET /api/documents/suggest-batches - Endpoint functional, returns empty suggestions
POST /api/batches/create - Creates batches successfully with document IDs
GET /api/batches/list - Lists batches with correct metadata
